STATIC STATE

open                NONE

cooked				inside oven OR ontop stove OR inside microwave

frozen				inside refrigerator

sliced				NONE

soaked				NONE

toggled				refrigerator

dusty				prob=1/3 if dustyable

stained				prob=1/3 if stainable

color-red			prob=1/3 if has-color

color-green			prob=1/3 if has-color

color-blue			prob=1/3 if has-color

size-large			prob=1/2 if has-size

size-small			prob=1/2 if has-size